{"tid":1553723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【存心謀殺】大埔後腦被打爆為中六生 遭警棍狂毆縫針肩掌骨折","createTime":"2019-09-08T16:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T17:16:21.000Z","uid":283080,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ee69f0219d0f9d6036295f072b381570f80ae028","tid":1553723,"uid":283080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8WB0P1B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8WB0P1B.jpg&h=a61c2a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hvp.healthalover.com/view2/6957/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhvp.healthalover.com%2Fview2%2F6957%2F&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=624e8751\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hvp.healthalover.com/view2/6957/</a><br />\n<br />\n//昨晚（7日）11時許，大埔人鏈示威活動演變成大型衝突，大批防暴警進入港鐵大埔墟站內堵截一批示威者，其中一名少年被五、六名警員按地制服並用警棍狂打，亂棍下少年頭破血流。消息指，<span style=\"color: red;\">該名少年頭部需縫針，肩膊及尾指骨折，情況嚴重</span>；據悉，被捕人士中，包括爆頭少年，有五人均來自區內同一所中學。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望同學仔吉人天相，早日康復！<br />\n班仆街黑警已經去到隨時殺人既地步！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家繼續關注８３１太子，新屋嶺，可疑命案事件！"},{"pid":"210032dcc7cceddb8be2a12f178610b9124af02f","tid":1553723,"uid":53524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"15歲讀中六"},{"pid":"0abe24d562d5b5851343190b8a40715c6f26c2e8","tid":1553723,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"210032dcc7cceddb8be2a12f178610b9124af02f","tid":1553723,"uid":53524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"15歲讀中六"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"年尾仔"},{"pid":"ca4e311a5bceeaf3ca373611fd813b422fa678b5","tid":1553723,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"dnlm"},{"pid":"6aa05a114c3aa09b47c7fc63b9043119d617c139","tid":1553723,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q